main event: On November 4, 1967 at approximately 3:15 p.m., an unidentified flying object was sighted over Lexington, Missouri.
interesting points: The object was described as dark oval in shape and approximately 30 to 40 feet in diameter,It was moving at an estimated speed of 400-500 mph,The incident involved two black and white photographs documenting the sighting,One photograph shows the object above a barn or farmhouse,The other photograph captures a snowy, wooded landscape.
